title: WATCH: Leslie Jones Is Hilarious As 'Black Trump' | Honey German | Power 105.1 FM
text:
share 
Leslie Jones is ready to play President Donald Trump and we know Trump is going to go all the way OFF. 
If Alec Baldwin playing the role ruffles Trump's feathered hair, we can only imagine what a black woman will do to him, LOL. 
We're here for it tho! A photo posted by HONEY GERMAN (@honeygerman) on Feb 12, 2017 at 6:01am PST Contact
